description: [IG Insights] This header is the name of a metric that appears on an educational info sheet for a particular post, story, video or promotion. This metric is the sum of all profile actions people take when they engage with this content.

name: profile_visits
title: Profile visits
description: The number of times your profile was visited.

name: reach
title: Accounts reached
description: The number of unique accounts that have seen this carousel container, at least once. Reach is different from impressions, which may include multiple views of your carousel container by the same accounts. This metric is estimated.

name: saved
title: Saved
description: The number of saves of your post.

name: shares
title: Shares
description: The number of shares of your post.

name: total_interactions
title: Post interactions
description: The number of likes, saves, comments and shares on your post minus the number of unlikes, unsaves and deleted comments.

name: views
title: Views
description: The number of times your post was played or displayed.

name: comments
title: Comments
description: The number of comments on your post.

name: follows
title: Follows
description: This is how many accounts started following you.

name: likes
title: Likes
description: The number of likes on your post.
